uly breathtaking. <strong>Rating:</strong> \u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</p>\n            <p><strong>Jane Smith:</strong> Very thrilling, but wish it was longer. <strong>Rating:</strong> \u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2606</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"review-form\">\n            <h3>Leave a Review</h3>\n            <form>\n                <label for=\"name\">Name:</label><br>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required><br><br>\n                <label for=\"review\">Review:</label><br>\n                <textarea id=\"review\" name=\"review\" rows=\"4\" cols=\"50\" required></textarea><br><br>\n                <label for=\"rating\">Rating:</label>\n                <select id=\"rating\" name=\"rating\">\n                    <option value=\"5\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</option>\n                    <option value=\"4\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2606</option>\n                    <option value=\"3\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2606\u2606</option>\n                    <option value=\"2\">\u2605\u2605\u2606\u2606\u2606</option>\n                    <option value=\"1\">\u2605\u2606\u2606\u2606\u2606</option>\n                </select><br><br>\n                <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit Review\">\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n### Key Elements:\n- **Video Player**: The `<video>` tag is used to embed the video. The `controls` attribute allows users to play, pause, and adjust the volume.\n- **Thumbnail**: The `poster` attribute in the `<video>` tag specifies the thumbnail image.\n- **Metadata**: Displayed using `<p>` tags for clarity and readability.\n- **Review Section**: Includes sample user reviews and a form for submitting new reviews. You can implement backend logic to handle form submissions as needed.\n\n### Customization:\n- Replace `\"thumbnail.jpg\"` and `\"video.mp4\"` with the actual paths to your thumbnail image and video file.\n- Update the metadata fields with the correc